      "releaseNotes": "Image generation and editing with Meta AI just got a big upgrade.\n\n• Save and reuse your own photos as references.\n• A wide range of image presets make it easy to create and edit images without prompting. \n• Meta AI taps into what's trending online, so it can pull in the memes and references you're thinking of.\n• Bring your exact vision to life through multi-turn prompting that’s as easy as having a conversation.\n• Sketch or write changes directly on your image, and Meta AI suggests edits making the process even easier.\n\n*Certain Meta AI features are only available in select countries and languages. Some of these features may roll out slowly over time.",
